8. What Happens Inside Flask?

Flask performs four major tasks.

Receive Request
        │
        ▼
Process Request
        │
        ▼
Call Gemini API
        │
        ▼
Return Response

Example:

Customer:

Recommend a pizza.

Flask sends this question to Gemini.

Gemini replies:

I recommend Margherita Pizza.

Flask returns this answer to the website.

